Placing his other hand on the wall next to the door, Cody gave it a mighty heave. With a shudder, the door came free,
slamming shut and almost making Cody close his balance. He ended up staring at Lulu, who stared back, blinking madly.
“You are a strange beast,” Cody told the little dog. Lulu wagged her tail, then resumed growling at the second door.
